{
  "stem": "13673.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One was this color, and the other one was red.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this one's from German to English, and the other one was from English to German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is how I got by the first few weeks that I was in England, because just to be able to say that the dog's under the table doesn't help you very much.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so if I wanted to communicate, I used the dictionaries and the other way around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, my mother got off in Wiesbaden, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then I was on my own on the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got to-- I guess it must have taken pretty much a full day when we finally arrived in the Hook of Holland in Holland, which is where we were to get on the boat to go to England.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got to the border of Germany and Holland, the German officials got off, and the Dutch officials came on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess we had to-- there must have been some other adults with us because they carried our papers, our passports.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all had numbers hanging around our necks and little cardboard things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And of course, the Dutch officials were much more human, even human-looking, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you OK?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What else?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if we ate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We must have had something on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know that we were greeted with stuff in Holland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were some women, Dutch women, there who were ready for us with--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was hot chocolate and cookies and stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it wasn't a full meal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think it was even sandwiches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we were taken onto the ferry boats.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was already evening.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
